Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:10.93,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:12.58,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eating properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.74,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.24,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You're busy, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.81,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:22.48,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It's far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:31.43,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:34.80,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why would it snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.19,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:44.64,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.57,Friend,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:33.09,sora-ep-title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(736,1)}Where Memories Live
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.51,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,First!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:43.95,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.38,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.57,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You were second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:48.08,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.35,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Who was faster than us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.85,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Whose group?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.43,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaka's group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.65,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:05.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, quick! Give me the stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:06.95,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:09.95,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your team has four people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.34,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:13.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:23.80,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, you're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:30.31,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,There's no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.60,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\N It's a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.72,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:38.33,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think orienteering is a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.67,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with orienteering!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.21,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,And where are the other two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:44.82,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.68,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.56,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you all want to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.68,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm happy just having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're the group leader. \NYou have to call Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.76,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, third one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.80,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's the next place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.56,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.87,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's behind the hotel by my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:24.93,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:28.98,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I think my shop is a checkpoint, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:32.37,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,My parents met with the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.86,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:40.52,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki, you shouldn't rush it. \NYou'll run out of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a home field advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:51.35,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We've been living here with that \Nstupid saucer this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:54.13,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We deserve this privilege!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Privilege?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.66,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,they have the same conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.40,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.88,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:10.12,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's rushing ahead again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.51,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We're enemies for now, so we'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.29,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.88,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you guys need this checkpoint, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:29.17,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning to go there later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Objective confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go report!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:50.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm technically the group leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.52,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.80,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Part of your duty as the leader is \Nto make use of enthusiastic troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.28,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:11.35,boat,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Motorboats
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.11,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.35,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:14.34,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen with Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:17.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of anything \NI might have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:22.48,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, hurry up. Let's go to the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're running now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.61,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:36.29,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we at Koharu's place yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.98,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You know where I live, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.04,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You should have paced yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:55.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's that thing's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's taking my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:02.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,With some mysterious, invisible something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.97,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You seem fine still.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:08.74,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the saucer's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:14.29,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:17.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.13,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.68,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:34.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.64,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.05,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Not really,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:44.03,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,but you know, I haven't had a \Nchance to talk to you much yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:52.11,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say that \Nthing when we first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.52,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bother coming back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.05,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shione-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:05.22,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Try calling me by my first name again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:07.42,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.79,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.76,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slap you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:20.23,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.44,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:29.90,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Shione's not really the \Ntalkative type to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:33.57,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't like that when \Nshe was little, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:35.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Have you known her for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:39.58,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Shione was born in this town, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:44.37,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what are you doing? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:49.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be hated \Nwhen I don't even know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.41,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, thanks for worrying for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:58.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still going to try to \Nbe friends with Shione-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.24,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.94,shop,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shiihara Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Togawa-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you lived here a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.89,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I did, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:43.10,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I was little, so I don't \Nremember about it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.76,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:51.12,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.42,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:56.61,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:57.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:58.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.51,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.37,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And here's our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.63,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.05,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.56,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.82,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:28.48,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:32.00,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go report to the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.11,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, hurry, stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:48.89,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What're you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.14,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.50,sora-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.55,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:05.56,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, monster-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.97,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Here, wipe your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.00,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, are you done with school yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.62,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm doing extracurricular work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:26.24,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,After school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I still have school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.35,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.61,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.36,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.00,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.34,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.88,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Can I keep her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I told you about her, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She's Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.40,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.87,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:02.45,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:10.66,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Shione,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.00,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,let's go to the next spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.67,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.83,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so cold to Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.76,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I hate her, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.98,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.21,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:36.40,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't think she'd \Nbe back now, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy units spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.46,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's five of us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.06,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have more than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.06,sora-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.56,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:54.17,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show them our power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:59.14,sora-main-top,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sucks to be with the noisy \None, huh, transfer kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.38,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.22,sora-main-top,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:04.41,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks we're stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:09.51,sora-main,Yu; Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:20.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The rest are past that \Nmountain over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,One more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.37,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:32.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit far, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.92,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you tired, Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:39.50,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:44.15,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You look the most tired \Nof all of us, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.01,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, where's Togawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:52.08,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She was walking behind \Nus until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:57.27,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.94,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She might just be slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.62,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.78,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we look for her together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.20,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.89,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:19.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki, take care of Noel for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Nonoka's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.21,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.37,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:38.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.40,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.06,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,How did you even get ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.92,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she took another route?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.29,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:52.66,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.26,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.19,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.60,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I guess now {\i1}I'm{\i0} lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.40,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:25.92,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:28.88,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.78,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:36.93,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.63,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.86,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We're already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.21,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:46.84,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, we're looking for the latecomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.30,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the transfer student \Nand that little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.09,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.27,Preschool,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyako \NKindergarten
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.41,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew this was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:14.70,Bus,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyako Kindergarten
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.53,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they found Shione-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.96,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I keep messing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:49.88,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Komiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.15,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.24,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.91,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since we've \Nall been together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.87,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.47,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We were all in separate classes \Nuntil last year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:08.33,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'd get complicated with \Ntwo twins in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.91,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you remember \Nback when there was—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:13.51,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.73,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,If she hadn't said what she did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.65,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't have called the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:23.07,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:24.52,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You can't forgive her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one that called the saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:31.53,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you being nice to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.32,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.51,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That song...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.70,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty good now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:25.11,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,from seven years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.84,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tokyo really far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.27,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.41,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:45.51,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,They asked me to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.50,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:48.93,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.85,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.86,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,They're left over. Why can't I have them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:57.47,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You can't. It's one each.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.99,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Here, catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.87,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.32,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.92,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:12.61,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.18,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.60,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:38.17,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Remember we talked about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:41.65,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If we all wish for it, \Na saucer will come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:45.66,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it said so in the saucer book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.11,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.95,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do something with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.42,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.79,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I might
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.17,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,not be able to see you once it's winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:04.38,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:08.68,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It would be hard to come \Nhere if it snows a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:13.50,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:18.65,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So, before it snows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:25.66,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka is {\i1}that{\i0} girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.86,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:32.46,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.91,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's helping me get rid of the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.17,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:40.05,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, she used to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.82,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,She said so herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.80,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:49.73,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,She made us help her call the saucer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.81,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,and then she left town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.27,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,For the past seven years
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:59.81,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,you've regretted it every time you've \Nlooked at the saucer, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:02.32,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:05.94,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,She comes back now, \Nand she calls us friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:08.07,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks we're stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:14.77,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:19.79,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But, we don't know if \Nthat was really Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.13,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:24.55,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:36.52,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.48,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I said it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:43.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,To call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.76,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:49.70,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:53.78,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.17,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:34.89,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of {\i1}Celestial Method{\i0}: \N"A Fragment of Emotions."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.45,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy!
